{"title":"Síndrome del lóbulo medio","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/General/Síndrome del lóbulo medio-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Síndrome del\\Nlóbulo medio","guid":"eTQXobbcDUDEidfq_lE2qQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Perlas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"- ¿Cuál es la principal causa del SLM?","guid":"17nMscMTfB8Y2AhMB9JnVQ","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"Atelectasia obstructiva crónica del LM por compresión extrínseca\\Nde ganglios linfáticos peribronquiales aumentados de tamaño. (1)","guid":"AfTDZjE4hP8I_7uMi6gizA","children":[]}]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"- ¿Qué patógenos están más\\Nfrecuentemente implicados en el SLM?","guid":"QaTpFmz0iRaGgsXDSMmqvA","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"Mycobacterium tuberculosis, Histoplasma capsulatum\\Ny Mycobacterium avium complex (MAC). (2)","guid":"uAZoNtdx-GdOKHGSsx2pdA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"0","text":"Definición:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"- El SLM es una entidad clínica que se caracteriza por atelectasia obstructiva crónica del lóbulo medio derecho\\Ndebido a compresión extrínseca de los ganglios linfáticos peribronquiales aumentados de tamaño. (1)","guid":"_E6jbSXrn82XMN2TFM_kEA","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"- Descrito por primera vez por Graham et al. en 1948. (3)","guid":"jNdk6JaazzXScGFo2eNPcA","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"- El LM es particularmente susceptible a la atelectasia debido a su anatomía:\\Ntiene un bronquio largo y estrecho, rodeado por ganglios linfáticos. (1)","guid":"1CergSMIuD2TY8dQb3DItw","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"- La compresión extrínseca del bronquio del LM por ganglios linfáticos\\Naumentados de tamaño lleva a obstrucción y atelectasia. (1)","guid":"dCeGqCVkOGdC7ATmXuWaKA","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"9","text":"- La atelectasia crónica predispone a infecciones\\Nrecurrentes y bronquiectasias. (2)","guid":"z8o0BLFqGaOjOAn6nF-gIw","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"- Incidencia exacta desconocida, pero es\\Nuna condición poco frecuente. (2)","guid":"c5GJmC7zmRgTLxf3gVvZJg","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"- Más común en niños y adultos jóvenes. (1)","guid":"T48BEuxtYr8qDr_8qo3gKw","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"13","text":"- Morbilidad significativa debido a infecciones\\Nrecurrentes y bronquiectasias. (2)","guid":"mCafxL7UlvHGTYGkIO-KnQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"0","text":"Factores\\Nde riesgo:","guid":"cKcCaFiaNty3d51QhBXxsQ","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"- Infección por M. tuberculosis, H. capsulatum, MAC. (2)","guid":"mdgNSKX2m8GozGQIKNse5A","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"- Inmunosupresión (VIH, uso de corticoides). (1)","guid":"CopXapjyFp3i-gsBbbaDlw","children":[]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"0","text":"Causas:","guid":"jmyBWxHfW4IH4zoPg7TWjw","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"- Infecciosas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"- Bacterianas:","guid":"_M538MtOpn4XblXIZSJSNw","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"- Mycobacterias:","guid":"Tk6SYzIGia5cWdVEJ95vKQ","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"- M. tuberculosis","guid":"Nh33_AevslgbQSlSU9M26A","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"- Micobacterias\\Nno tuberculosas:","guid":"-NtCbgeFTaLvHNJV3cWMTA","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"- M. avium complex (MAC)","guid":"YkL83Ab0DVGZyzR76hw7OQ","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"- M. kansasii","guid":"oLzOpnjsoY1fulUp6h_81g","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"25","text":"- M. xenopi","guid":"ukstkXo4Qs_P-Y-jR3l3oQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"22","text":"- Otras\\Nbacterias:","guid":"BMVGI7YhuCUeizmRYw-BdQ","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"- Streptococcus pneumoniae","guid":"4HLoPadZmwHXodoKsSFFGQ","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"29","text":"- Haemophilus influenzae","guid":"mrgYi72yGrL3ljVVIlFCCg","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"29","text":"- Staphylococcus aureus","guid":"C_wVhpTCuoPOa0L3-AdzJg","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"29","text":"- Pseudomonas aeruginosa","guid":"Y9rzRxAZ3SDFJ2vJ6E6D7g","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"29","text":"- Nocardia spp.","guid":"qDLtLfuL4_KrT3UBXZI0Hg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"21","text":"- Fúngicas:","guid":"mgzVnP7i1Sz97H7yxNXm7g","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"- Histoplasma capsulatum","guid":"w9k6LKecXCFP07dIo3vhOQ","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"35","text":"- Cryptococcus neoformans","guid":"zc94rjMx16VW4tQ0L_EJ4Q","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"35","text":"- Aspergillus spp.","guid":"Ds3slyXqDf3JhyqJZCPlkA","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"35","text":"- Coccidioides immitis","guid":"kFtu3ug1Mi0panTEFw6j2w","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"35","text":"- Blastomyces dermatitidis","guid":"vrA471Mtbtm3M0vVGCXctg","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"21","text":"- Parasitarias:","guid":"VyPztYENfLFZ4yoY9kReQQ","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"- Ascaris lumbricoides","guid":"_H2V2Q9gabIr8d0-iJ2Xig","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"- Strongyloides stercoralis","guid":"Sinn0MYWVWSY_E9wyePjzw","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"21","text":"- Virales (poco\\Nfrecuente):","guid":"Vp19PbWPxBOxASWvXMkZjg","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"- Virus respiratorio sincicial","guid":"O0cJETiu9uxlsKzxlJehqw","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"- Adenovirus","guid":"sM39SPZp3woPdCHYFYc6Ag","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"44","text":"- Influenza","guid":"rsiknVaaMIUuUOzw5CTkcQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"20","text":"- No infecciosas:","guid":"htj2JRrxD2vxP5y3OkdRsw","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"- Enfermedades\\Ngranulomatosas:","guid":"ST3bsyMGrsyPQAcnYIpU7w","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"- Sarcoidosis","guid":"qmNk6hdo07S0Y12FByGoRg","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"- Granulomatosis con poliangeítis (Wegener)","guid":"lxgZWYOrjBpnItcqIrQw5w","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"48","text":"- Enfermedades por exposición\\Na polvos inorgánicos:","guid":"-ika6Hg2lANPSCClZF4eoA","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"- Silicosis","guid":"JHCAmmXyQeQ3-RacZWEnoA","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"- Beriliosis","guid":"7-nzyz_RX1iW3CAq91dkaQ","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"52","text":"- Neumoconiosis del trabajador del carbón","guid":"lXa42Sr0qYwVc0Z5uwjb4Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"48","text":"- Enfermedades por\\Nexposición a polvos orgánicos:","guid":"ADmSscRFeLWbN5qXrxoBkw","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"- Neumonitis por hipersensibilidad","guid":"FYmx9MZyI030v0J0364RlA","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"- Pulmón del granjero","guid":"CkwiUrncjXUV5-Wszh4HUg","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"56","text":"- Pulmón del cuidador de aves","guid":"Ir5CQ7J9ElC1cIL089m3OQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"48","text":"- Enfermedades\\Npor depósito:","guid":"L3KSNCdfVGjIFAN9LDRAOw","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"- Amiloidosis","guid":"-SMkXTArafIEQSkie_AWjA","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"- Enfermedad por depósito de cadenas ligeras","guid":"1CblHQQZiOKzL6X5zVsJxw","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"- Enfermedad por depósito de cadenas pesadas","guid":"dBLD4yKxsI4n0g-5XPGufA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"20","text":"- Otras:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"- Obstrucción por cuerpo extraño","guid":"lKh9qBMSis4JKEsatsMhDQ","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"- Obstrucción por tumor endobronquial (carcinoide, carcinoma de células escamosas)","guid":"gKkpQEnKdfTmBzqFboZ6Jg","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"- Obstrucción por tumor extrabronquial (linfoma, cáncer metastásico)","guid":"azQQ9G3gDz7hrYkv9X0SOw","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"64","text":"- Obstrucción por anormalidades vasculares (sling de la arteria pulmonar, arco aórtico doble)","guid":"8LOquOf3rAzOmPc8_iSFtA","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"64","text":"- Aspiración recurrente","guid":"vkoWs44PB2tMXZFGsPCrTA","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"64","text":"- Reflujo gastroesofágico","guid":"UNlPDC30NkASAC85abV5SA","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"64","text":"- Deficiencia de alfa-1 antitripsina","guid":"ie49T1wtl4hWkKfygjDcBQ","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"64","text":"- Fibrosis quística","guid":"bsQU4pxZ32MGC98tnGqmqQ","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"64","text":"- Discinesia ciliar primaria","guid":"yBj04ArNNtwIl2g1M49s6g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"74","parent":"0","text":"Clínica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"- Antecedentes: infección previa, inmunosupresión. (1)","guid":"RVkImYBrYxnJVfp-nonciA","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"74","text":"- Cuadro clínico:","guid":"D9SNh0PgTTR1iS1EKg6V1w","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"- Tos crónica","guid":"5IxlLRWKFqxXm1JuCEQBvw","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"- Expectoración purulenta","guid":"WsCoYKNVIrVKId9xd66S2Q","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"76","text":"- Disnea","guid":"vjgXfeP79wJY4wWjIRoqhw","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"76","text":"- Dolor torácico","guid":"zkj5_4NjveFLxi4IbeGs9g","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"76","text":"- Fiebre, escalofríos, sudoración nocturna (2)","guid":"OUhdse8--xWl7e7WJWO55g","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"74","text":"- Triada clásica: tos, expectoración purulenta, opacidad del LM en la radiografía de tórax. (3)","guid":"aa-yX2sETObAbtfqeJS_eA","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"74","text":"- Factores de mal pronóstico: inmunosupresión, retraso en el diagnóstico y tratamiento. (2)","guid":"H6sz7kPIcM30HBzOWcEuWw","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"74","text":"- Complicaciones: bronquiectasias, hemoptisis, fistula broncopleural, empiema. (1)","guid":"LIvadShnlVB-Y5QEdHR1mA","children":[]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"0","text":"Estudio:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"- Radiografía de tórax: atelectasia del LM, opacidad en \"dedo de guante\". Sensibilidad 70%. (2)","guid":"t01w108V0nBP9aWSr-jEhQ","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"- TC de tórax: atelectasia del LM, bronquiectasias, ganglios linfáticos aumentados de tamaño. Sensibilidad 95%. (2)","guid":"hgfQHknNLrLZUile-BqtCw","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"- Broncoscopia: estenosis u obstrucción del bronquio del LM, secreciones purulentas. (1)","guid":"YxFv1XoWCn43FCw_Qbrkrg","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"85","text":"- Cultivo de expectoración o lavado broncoalveolar: identificación del patógeno. (2)","guid":"IBRZIg0zbAAiItjozypW0w","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"- Diagnóstico de trabajo: SLM basado en clínica y radiografía de tórax. (2)","guid":"LfjSNWxoaGxapZ8pLQO-Dw","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"- Gold standard: broncoscopia con biopsia y cultivo. (1)","guid":"7sSTjsOHUwlmnAJwiJ4Qgg","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"- Criterios\\Ndiagnósticos:","guid":"1NHSUObedqh5v5JwLB72sw","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"1. Clínica compatible","guid":"9v-x2LJzbROJQJh1ee8TSA","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"93","text":"2. Atelectasia del LM en la radiografía de tórax o TC","guid":"h6slHUkPyIV2-ETW6QcQNA","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"93","text":"3. Exclusión de otras causas (1)","guid":"Xm_B5Do7gIpxubqEfGY0fg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"0","text":"Diagnósticos\\Ndiferenciales:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"- Síndrome de condensación\\Npulmonar:","guid":"h2IbDBMSuCgTOWTrL7WmrQ","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"- Neumonía adquirida en la comunidad","guid":"IBvnm5hFp-cPL3vPl24kWw","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"98","text":"- Tuberculosis pulmonar","guid":"H-aRS5HX-JCGerrM5LTPSA","children":[]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"97","text":"- Micosis pulmonar","guid":"mcFvuYxbMc56vXlq9jxRbQ","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"97","text":"- Bronquiectasias infectadas (2)","guid":"Fk9xB6oh3Hlj3sYELHF1_w","children":[]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"- Objetivo: erradicar la infección, prevenir recurrencias, manejar las complicaciones. (1)","guid":"r4dXVGYLqIGhs3P6MU1h1w","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"103","text":"- No farmacológico:","guid":"1X7oZSChAWpEK4p94-1_3Q","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"- Fisioterapia respiratoria","guid":"aNxWvTxWYKWp9Mky5YYSjg","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"- Drenaje postural (2)","guid":"uogtgb66DkqyVi5DbivM7g","children":[]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"103","text":"- Farmacológico:","guid":"JEhr9ntXWF1J2jt0kRDndA","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"- 1ª línea: antibióticos según el patógeno identificado. Ej: para MAC, claritromicina 500 mg c/12h\\N+ etambutol 15 mg/kg/día + rifampicina 10 mg/kg/día, por 12 meses. (4)","guid":"Dzr3RalVv83sEYkjcUKN9A","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"- 2ª línea: glucocorticoides sistémicos si hay compresión significativa por ganglios. Ej:\\Nprednisona 1 mg/kg/día por 1-2 semanas, luego disminuir gradualmente. (2)","guid":"VVcTRPUMPsaNSVddtC2FoA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"111","parent":"0","text":"Seguimiento y\\Npronóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"- Radiografía de tórax y espirometría cada 3 meses. (2)","guid":"XxZa95rZJ5CK48TDCdPx6g","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"111","text":"- TC de tórax si mala evolución clínica o radiográfica. (1)","guid":"cp-h2FnvqHFm6onB-gEZhw","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"111","text":"- Seguimiento por neumólogo, kinesiólogo, infectólogo. (2)","guid":"C42t0zqpbvcGfauDiypy5Q","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"111","text":"- Pronóstico variable según la causa y las complicaciones. Mortalidad <5% con tratamiento adecuado y oportuno. (1)","guid":"nb0GWHcxwoIagYO59gnaww","children":[]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"0","text":"Prevención:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"- Tratamiento precoz y adecuado de las infecciones pulmonares. (2)","guid":"Bp5HOtyesv7haEEiXwB1zQ","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"116","text":"- Evitar la inmunosupresión innecesaria. (1)","guid":"7cJ_mBP7R1s-EkZa4CpUCQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"119","parent":"0","text":"Tamizaje:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"- No hay recomendaciones específicas de tamizaje para el SLM. (2)","guid":"Jw0Kjq7aw0PL1HbES3KNjA","children":[]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"0","text":"Aspectos\\NGeriátricos:","guid":"QORECf7DqDWjTS2qmGS8pQ","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"- Mayor riesgo de complicaciones y mortalidad. (1)","guid":"Xi17VnuPSwUrwV0mY6WTFA","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"- Ajustar dosis de antibióticos según función renal. (4)","guid":"epabB4ygCk1ekAkSiuVnRA","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"121","text":"- Considerar interacciones farmacológicas y polifarmacia. (2)","guid":"jA5rTTPuc0iVIJOsWyuXNA","children":[]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"0","text":"• Definición:","guid":"YRqBBTRHuqOM5YjjExnTRQ","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"• Entidad clínica infrecuente (↘ reconocimiento clínico).","guid":"p8kzG6qFu9wJnqFVGHPeSg","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"• Atelectasia recurrente o fija del lóbulo medio derecho (patognomónico).","guid":"3s7-nyQzBSY5vCJW6uk_fw","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"125","text":"• Subdivisión en 2 tipos: obstructivo y no obstructivo.","guid":"LvzB8f8m0MQQz4y9I8ihWQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"0","text":"• Etiología:","guid":"WBaG5n-NK4fM__hNqjxwmw","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"1. Tipo obstructivo:","guid":"Jb1t4H2mxmLvkSslRy0LFQ","children":[{"id":"131","parent":"130","text":"• Causa: compresión extrínseca del bronquio del lóbulo medio derecho.","guid":"e202is4oqnm5P6GjG3VWmQ","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"130","text":"• Origen:","guid":"UScCGyy6z0Skhn1Ueg8NcQ","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"• Linfadenopatía peribronquial (enf. granulomatosas, infecciones fúngicas, micobacterias).","guid":"tH7t5obbQuvmvqXroqWxqg","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"132","text":"• Tumores (hamartomas, cáncer de pulmón primario, metástasis).","guid":"iQ-5nazqkTdsjq4XF2ucpw","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"132","text":"• Otros (sarcoidosis, aspiración, tapones de moco, broncolitos).","guid":"dxMiwCutY-WEMlVt-ILt4A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"136","parent":"129","text":"2. Tipo no obstructivo:","guid":"iocSsZZqk9At_Qni3eJZjQ","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"• Sin obstrucción detectable en broncoscopia.","guid":"mdx8vYgx1E5-3h6Ww-mSdQ","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"136","text":"• Hipótesis: ventilación colateral ineficaz del lóbulo medio → predisposición a atelectasia.","guid":"etC0IaFFf-O9SEsC57jrfQ","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"136","text":"• Asociado a hipoventilación transitoria en contextos inflamatorios crónicos\\N(fibrosis quística, infecciones, infartos pulmonares, quistes broncopulmonares).","guid":"hdT-WD9cpLpdMgwR-Hznzg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"0","text":"Right Middle Lobe\\NSyndrome (MLS)","guid":"zvcG8bErU0KxXOMikqUvXw","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"• Epidemiología:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"• Datos limitados.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"140","text":"• Ratio\\Nmujeres:hombres\\N>1.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"140","text":"• Mujeres presentan\\NMLS a mayor edad.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"140","text":"• El tipo no obstructivo\\N(inflamatorio crónico) es el\\Nmás común (>60% casos).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"140","text":"• Evaluación:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"140","text":"• Historia clínica\\Ndetallada + sospecha\\Nalta.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"140","text":"• Imagenología (Rx, TC tórax) →\\Nopacificación lóbulo medio.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"140","text":"• Broncoscopia: para identificar\\Nobstrucción (tipo obstructivo) o\\Ndescartarla (tipo no obstructivo).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"140","text":"• Manejo:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"140","text":"1. Tipo obstructivo:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"140","text":"• Resolución de la causa\\Nsubyacente (ej. resección\\Ntumoral, manejo infecciones).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"140","text":"2. Tipo no obstructivo:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"140","text":"• Fisioterapia respiratoria.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"140","text":"• Tratamiento de\\Ninfecciones subyacentes.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"140","text":"• En casos refractarios:\\Nlobectomía del lóbulo medio.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"140","text":"• Importancia del equipo\\Ninterprofesional:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"140","text":"• Colaboración estrecha entre\\Nneumólogos, cirujanos torácicos,\\Nradiólogos, y terapeutas respiratorios.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"140","text":"• Comunicación efectiva →\\Nmanejo adecuado y oportuno.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"160","parent":"0","text":"• Fisiopatología:","guid":"5daSNOVghtW5j-TACXb5gw","children":[{"id":"161","parent":"160","text":"• Tipo obstructivo:","guid":"KifIgvvGsONp9GGv9WPKOA","children":[]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"0","text":"Right Middle Lobe\\NSyndrome (MLS)","guid":"yDDgLIKW-nrMqKavO_uZSA","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"• Disminución del diámetro endoluminal en\\Nbronquio lóbulo medio derecho (↘ diámetro\\Ncomparado con otros bronquios lobares).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"162","text":"• Compresión\\Nextraluminal o\\Nintraluminal.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"162","text":"• Predisposición en mujeres (↘\\Ndiámetro endoluminal\\Ncomparado con hombres).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"162","text":"• Fisuras del lóbulo medio y língula\\N→ ↘ ventilación colateral → ↘\\Nclearance mucoso.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"162","text":"• Tipo no obstructivo:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"162","text":"• Hipoventilación transitoria →\\Natelectasia recurrente.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"162","text":"• Sin obstrucción visible\\Nen broncoscopia.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"162","text":"• Historia clínica y\\Nexamen físico:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"162","text":"• Síntomas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"162","text":"• Tos crónica,\\Nhemoptisis, disnea.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"162","text":"• Neumonía recurrente (difícil\\Nde tratar, intrusiva).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"162","text":"• Examen físico:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"162","text":"• Sibilancias, roncus, ↓ sonidos\\Nrespiratorios, taquipnea, diaforesis (en\\Nneumonía concomitante).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"162","text":"• Casos raros: falla para prosperar, caquexia\\N(según etiología subyacente).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"162","text":"• Evaluación:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"162","text":"• Imagenología:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"162","text":"• Rx tórax PA y lateral → posible\\Nsigno de silueta (borde cardíaco\\Nderecho oscurecido).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"162","text":"• TC de tórax y broncoscopia →\\Nevaluación causa subyacente.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"162","text":"• Laboratorio:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"162","text":"• Hemograma completo.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"162","text":"• Cultivos bacterianos específicos\\N(para manejo dirigido).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"162","text":"• Tratamiento y manejo:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"162","text":"• General:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"162","text":"• Optimización función pulmonar\\N(mucolíticos, fisioterapia,\\Nbroncodilatadores, ATB).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"162","text":"• Terapia antibiótica dirigida (↗\\NPseudomonas spp.).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"162","text":"• Tipo obstructivo:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"162","text":"• Broncoscopia → remoción cuerpos\\Nextraños o tumores intrabronquiales.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"162","text":"• Posible intervención quirúrgica\\N(lobectomía en casos refractarios).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"162","text":"• Tipo no obstructivo:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"162","text":"• Fisioterapia respiratoria y manejo de\\Ninfecciones subyacentes.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"162","text":"• Diagnóstico diferencial:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"162","text":"• Fibrosis quística, bronquiectasias, aspergilosis,\\Nsecuestro pulmonar, TB, asma, EPOC,\\Ninmunodeficiencias, trastornos ciliarios.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"162","text":"• Mejora de resultados\\Ndel equipo de salud:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"162","text":"• Detección precisa:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"162","text":"• Implicación activa de\\Nneumólogos en manejo y\\Ndiagnóstico (broncoscopia).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"162","text":"• Educación al paciente\\N(rehabilitación pulmonar,\\Nfisioterapia).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"162","text":"• Stewardship antibiótico:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"162","text":"• Consultas farmacéuticas para manejo de\\Ninfecciones multirresistentes.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"162","text":"• De-escalación rápida con\\Ncultivos apropiados.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"162","text":"• Coordinación\\Ninterprofesional:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"162","text":"• Educación, monitorización de\\Ntratamiento, adherencia (enfermería).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"162","text":"• Vacunación adecuada,\\Nprevención exposición a\\Nquímicos nocivos y tabaco.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"205","parent":"0","text":"Referencias:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"0","text":"12. Fuente relacionada con la\\Nfisiopatología del MLS.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"0","text":"13. Fuente relacionada con\\Nla ventilación colateral y\\Nclearance mucoso.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"0","text":"14. Fuente adicional sobre historia\\Nclínica y diagnóstico diferencial.","guid":"","children":[]}]},"node_count":208,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/General","filename":"Síndrome del lóbulo medio-2024-1","id":"map_872","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Síndrome del lóbulo medio-2024-1"}